a’s. Of je nu kiest voor de standaard iPhone 17 camera, de dunne iPhone Air camera of de camera’s van de iPhone 17 Pro en iPhone 17 Pro Max, je foto’s en video’s zien er ontzettend scherp en kleurrijk uit. Met meer megapixels en slimme software levert Apple opnieuw een iPhone-model met top-camerakwaliteit. Zo leg je eenvoudig je mooiste momenten vast, of dat nu een snelle selfie is of een vakantie vol herinneringen. In deze blog vertellen we je meer over de verschillende camera’s van alle nieuwe iPhone 17 modellen.",{"title":126},{"id":1297,"objectType":9,"contentType":300,"name":1298,"isVerticalView":20,"theme":137,"image":1299,"isImagePositionRight":20,"title":1310,"navigation":1311,"heading":1353},"IK7u9YvrlmZ5TbSFyAfS2","iPhone Air review - Beleef - iPhone - forwardlink",{"id":1300,"objectType":9,"contentType":92,"name":1301,"image":1302},"7iixTGr84bljGon7Z4exf0","iPhone 17 Air review - media",{"id":1303,"objectType":96,"title":1301,"description":50,"file":1304},"MbA6NiiCI5wj7TYEdeyZH",{"url":1305,"details":1306,"fileName":1309,"contentType":106},"//images.ctfassets.net/zuadwp3l2xby/MbA6NiiCI5wj7TYEdeyZH/e2f1dec925c72acb56de7b34662d8621/Air_review__1_.png",{"size":1307,"image":1308},484467,{"width":1089,"height":510},"Air review (1).png","iPhone Air review",[1312],{"id":1313,"objectType":9,"contentType":55,"name":1314,"text":1315,"type":85,"iconPosition":405,"linkPresentation":86,"link":1316,"target":79,"anchorSection":65},"6U9OYcSTFD6MkQTmzXLq3L","Naar het blog met iPhone Air review - forwardlink - /beleef/blog/iphone-air-review","Naar het blog met de iPhone Air review",{"id":1317,"objectType":9,"contentType":1099,"name":1310,"title":1310,"breadcrumbPosition":320,"slug":1318,"type":13,"productLabel":1319,"audienceLabel":1326,"phaseLabel":1333,"publishDate":1221,"estimatedReadTime":1158,"media":1339,"siteWideMedia":28,"previewImage":1346,"spotlight":20,"heading":1351,"intro":1352,"anchorMenuEnabled":28,"smartAppBanner":377},"Vjkaew6cUtpSt8CrQOqS8","/beleef/blog/