2532,"description":50,"file":2537},"SWXujcn7vT7RZsqh5btgY",{"url":2538,"details":2539,"fileName":2494,"contentType":1142},"//images.ctfassets.net/zuadwp3l2xby/SWXujcn7vT7RZsqh5btgY/a15ccc8790ec1053d062bbea8a46e21b/Galaxy_S25_vs_iPhone_Blog.jpg",{"size":2490,"image":2540},{"width":2492,"height":2493},{"id":2534,"objectType":9,"contentType":92,"name":2532,"image":2542},{"id":2536,"objectType":96,"title":2532,"description":50,"file":2543},{"url":2538,"details":2544,"fileName":2494,"contentType":1142},{"size":2490,"image":2545},{"width":2492,"height":2493},"In september van 2024 is de Apple iPhone 16 op de markt gebracht. Dat is Apple’s laatste smartphone. Maar ook Samsung heeft niet stilgezeten. In januari 2025 lanceerden ze de Samsung Galaxy S25. Van beide telefoons bestaan meerdere varianten. De iPhone 16, de 16 Plus, de 16 Pro en de 16 Pro Max aan Apple’s kant. En aan Samsung’s kant de Galaxy S25, S25 Plus en S25 Ultra. We leggen de modellen onder de loep in deze vergelijking! ",{"title":126},{"id":2549,"objectType":9,"contentType":300,"name":2550,"isVerticalView":20,"image":2551,"isImagePositionRight":20,"title":2565,"navigation":2566,"heading":2615},"4IUJhDqoqK6vGg6tRK0TG0","Wat is Galaxy AI? - Galaxy AI Beleef - image - forwardlink",{"id":2552,"objectType":9,"contentType":92,"name":2553,"image":2554,"altText":2563,"alt":2564},"3KfjxBIluw8TwEGTird037","Actie Samsung S24-series, Z Fold5, Z Flip5 + cashback",{"id":2555,"objectType":96,"title":2556,"description":50,"file":2557},"3FO7PwG1SEkdpOuDHSDlFH","infoblock afgelopen acties - samsung cashback",{"url":2558,"details":2559,"fileName":2562,"contentType":106},"//images.ctfassets.net/zuadwp3l2xby/3FO7PwG1SEkdpOuDHSDlFH/6de75ffd7bf032b9ad5c5880d8f1b7ca/infoblock_afgelopen_acties_-_samsung_cashback.png",{"size":2560,"image":2561},1718009,{"width":1118,"height":807},"infoblock afgelopen acties - samsung cashback.png","5 Samsung telefoons van de S24-series, Z Fold5 en Z Flip5 met de tekst: ‘Galaxy AI is here’ op de scher